"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"It‚Äôs 8:22 and I‚Äôm watching TV and scanning Discord servers and scrolling Twitter and thinking about little black boxes with lists of words on them - when I get a notification.\\n\\nNew tweet from [Loot Character](https://twitter.com/LootCharacter). There will be an announcement tonight.\\n\\n20 minutes later, a cryptic message in the Discord:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1SewzaeZk0bM7RYsebJmL.png?height=164&width=458)\\n\\n### Rewinding a little bit\\n\\nLoot Character was launched on September 9th via Tweet:\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/LootCharacter/status/1436003545476653067?s=20](https://twitter.com/LootCharacter/status/1436003545476653067?s=20)\\n\\n[lootcharacter.com](https://www.lootcharacter.com/) is simple mint site.\\n\\nYou connect your wallet. You see a 8-bit character version of your Loot bag. You scroll down, and find a message:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/x5p-TjlMR1FjFHOMxrbYK.png?height=1159&width=1456)\\n\\nLoot Character is an associative NFT, which means once you choose a guild, and mint a Loot Character NFT, that NFT is tied to your Loot bag. Wherever your Loot goes, so goes the character.\\n\\nThere‚Äôs a .2 ETH mint fee. ‚Öì goes to your chosen guild, ‚Öì goes to a gameplay treasury (where it can be found, earned, won, or stolen), and ‚Öì goes to funding future game development.\\n\\nThe choice indeed decides your fate.\\n\\nYou mint your Loot character. You check OpenSea and see it in your wallet. And you see something else in your wallet. Another NFT:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1yoG8u1hLuIQDmBVbQVpG.png?height=1103&width=1456)\\n\\n*‚ÄúYou may answer the riddle at mint‚Äôs end.‚Äù*\\n\\n### Back to the story\\n\\n35 minutes after the cryptic message, the game begins:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5GyBY3Ve9NacDvvFGAOY4.png?height=256&width=522)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/HQrA0qtBb6PjzOGHdnHa9.png?height=1140&width=1412)\\n\\nThe note changed. The riddle was revealed.\\n\\nAt this point the Loot Character Discord had one channel. The guesses started coming. Fast. Wild ideas, reading-way-too-far-into-it ideas, ideas that ultimately were pretty close to right.\\n\\nThen, the gamemakers opened gated guild channels. (You can only access your Loot Character guild‚Äôs channel.)\\n\\nThe Unknowable guild started working together. 4 minutes later, lunarmayor figured out the code - **ethereum**.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XcZMwLuNwIzsaZ5RtelLE.png?height=968&width=1074)\\n\\nThen scotato and lunarmayor figured out how to input the code.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/RNcatY1CKKG7m68O-xQmv.png?height=1098&width=1116)\\n\\n*‚ÄúYou must connect your wallet to continue‚Ä¶‚Äù*\\n\\nlunarmayor and scotato couldnn‚Äôt sign into their wallets to continue, so I went to lootcharacter.com -\\n\\nI typed **ethereum** -\\n\\nMy screen turned black -\\n\\nAnd I got a message:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/qDjF-fZ9DrIrH2FlWl1Zz.png?height=1140&width=1456)\\n\\nlunarmayor and scotato finally got their wallets connected, and saw this message when they entered the code:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kIxF3EMEaaUt4u-TT8Kh3.png?height=560&width=1456)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WrSb7WHzWUVGmVB3Fj7db.png?height=445&width=393)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9pf04m9VusxlhN1ThhbH-.png?height=524&width=730)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JZgSvqyRYokEN-D9J9Q-z.png?height=116&width=658)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YBqfSFcdqBCUrQDKT-S8Y.png?height=584&width=1290)\\n\\nI put out a tweet. [@heyhaigh](https://twitter.com/heyhaigh) DMd me, joined the Discord, and we brought him up to speed:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/bXSKEQVEz5er_VliS2ofx.png?height=582&width=550)\\n\\nHe got the last key. Unknowable guild got all 8 keys.\\n\\nRound 1 was over in 2 hours 2 minutes.\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/LootCharacter/status/1439811704729350145?s=20](https://twitter.com/LootCharacter/status/1439811704729350145?s=20)\\n\\n### Epilogue\\n\\n### ü§Ø\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/V1RllGiAxfzdxg-0-uID2.png?height=270&width=1326)\\n\\n### üëÄ\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4EpDXoixCRiqmv1oZ9B2n.png?height=288&width=1322)\\n\\n### Aftermath\\n\\nSince solving the first riddle together, the Unknowable guild has been busy.\\n\\nWe bought our own ENS.\\n\\nRemember how 1/3 of the mint fee goes to each guild? That ETH, plus the 2 ETH reward is now in a shared Unknowable guild Gnosis Safe wallet.\\n\\nWe even have a Snapshot for decision making.\\n\\nTo be clear, I don‚Äôt know any of these people. I don‚Äôt know real names, genders, what they look like, what they do for a living. Nothing except Discord handles, Twitter handles, and PFPs.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/BKVSEHoLKxYn9edtCHweL.png?height=998&width=1166)\\n\\nWe share alpha:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Eg9VIwt8T-Kq_fxZotpCY.png?height=257&width=1456)\\n\\nWe fire each other up:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Y27LXKUdRr1kZuWlcUoHp.png?height=780&width=896)\\n\\nWe designed sigils in a shared Figma page:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pnqo4ETkiGFwVxJ0Hjp9B.png?height=1492&width=1456)\\n\\nWe voted on a sigil, which will be minted as a an associative NFT that can only be claimed by members of the Unknowable guild.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DhJBUWAMr_mGtN0HZOgPW.png?height=892&width=892)\\n\\n### Roadmap\\n\\nUnknowable guild has all 8 keys from the first riddle. We have a treasury with a considerable amount of ETH in it. What are our options? What can we do? Here are some ideas:\\n\\n* Continue playing the game and stacking ETH\\n* Buy NFTs with our ETH\\n* Mint and sell our own NFTs\\n* Buy a floor CrypToad\\n* Donate a percentage to charity\\n* Fund public goods\\n* Redistribute the funds to everyone and go our separate ways\\n* Build our own metaverse game\\n* There have been 197 Loot Characters minted. We could recruit the remaining 7582 Loot Bag holders to mint Unknowable Guild Characters. That would send .06 ETH per bag to our treasury, adding roughly 504 ETH to the Unknowable warchest\\n\\n### As I was writing this‚Ä¶\\n\\nLoot Character revealed Riddle #2:\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/LootCharacter/status/1449932882110152707?s=20](https://twitter.com/LootCharacter/status/1449932882110152707?s=20)\\n\\n### Roadmap (Revised)\\n\\n* Win Riddle #2\",\"timestamp\":1634680393,\"title\":\"üß© The First Riddle\",\"publication\":\"lootproject\"},\"digest\":\"nudj_wefJtd33SxhEPnFtX35mO2B2yIpwmocXdvY5u4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x596E7fe8a3FD3AB4dEdC227c848569a0265828Ff\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ByJeg1S1c34ilbhy55WfevteB0plXI2MIZUMtvZsGDs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xi_rpycaxw7GBUUxhkMHlMMufIU71i9YWQ_Xpo-gNhc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"cQUJhs_ivepdJ-fNWEEYcW-uGM8-3_pDUEmvpDJNgRfsMO8uJg4o9tVoDJYlOtT6_4ABvHul8Yp9Taa7Ahxtpg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x378e51a11a397d009ebb47aad60f065fbe03a2e47562df3ec897ea19e5df82d50f97849ebb8fe1c2b9acc5614d09707c252f51e350f358d5ca5a7671588f8f3b1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on lootproject.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ByJeg1S1c34ilbhy55WfevteB0plXI2MIZUMtvZsGDs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xi_rpycaxw7GBUUxhkMHlMMufIU71i9YWQ_Xpo-gNhc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}}